3 | website= group73historians.com | language= ar | trans-title= All You Want To Know About \"The Defresoar Gab Battle\" | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191210111729/https://www.group73historians.com/%D8%AD%D8%B1%D8%A8-%D8%A3%D9%83%D8%AA%D9%88%D8%A8%D8%B1/144-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%80%D8%AB%D9%80%D8%BA%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%8A%D9%87-%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D9%87%D8%A7%D9%8A%D9%87 | archive-date= 2019-12-10 | url-status= live | access-date= 2020-03-07 | ref= Gab_Battle | df= dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"1973_Suez_Map\">{{cite web | url= https://www.steelbeasts.com/topic/12553-suez-canal-1973-war-maps/ | title= Suez Canal 1973 war maps | date= 2019 | website= steelbeasts.com | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200308024534/https://www.steelbeasts.com/topic/12553-suez-canal-1973-war-maps/ | archive-date= 2020-03-08 | url-status= live | access-date= 2020-03-08 | ref= 1973_Suez_Map | df= dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"1999_Razoux\">{{cite journal | last1= Razoux | first1= Pierre | author-link= Pierre Razoux | date= 1999-06-21 | title= La guerre du Kippour d'octobre 1973 | trans-title= The Yom Kippur War of October 1973 | series= CAMPAGNES ET ST | language= fr | volume= Book 30 | publisher= [[Economica]] | asin= B0160JG4RM | isbn= 978-2717838138 | issn= 0013-0427 | eissn= 1468-0335 | jstor= 130427 | lccn= 22023854 | oclc= 878432332 | ol= OL12529082M | ref= 1999_Razoux | df= dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"2000_Gawrych\">{{cite book | last1= Gawrych | first1= George W. | date= 2000-03-30 | title= The Albatross of Decisive Victory: War and Policy Between Egypt and Israel in the 1967 and 1973 Arab-Israeli Wars | url= https://archive.org/details/arabisraeliwaral00gawr | url-status= live | series= Contributions in Military Studies | language= en | volume= Book 188 | publisher= [[Greenwood Publishing Group|Praeger]] | isbn= 978-0313313028 | oclc= 912514280 | ol= OL9418338M | access-date= 2020-03-08 | via= [[Internet Arc